summary: This is a forwarded email from July 8, 2019, within the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS), regarding a potential victim who called with information about Jeffrey Epstein. The email is being circulated among prosecutors and FBI personnel.

events.title: Potential Victim Call to CSOs
events.description: A female from Pennsylvania called the CSOs (likely Criminal Section or Complaint Section) and provided information about Jeffrey Epstein, leaving a return phone number.

keyFacts: On July 8, 2019, a potential victim from Pennsylvania contacted authorities with information about Jeffrey Epstein.
The communication was an internal email within the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS), forwarded to FBI personnel.
The document reference EFTA00155547 appears to be a case or phone number related to this tip.
The email indicates active investigation and information gathering about Epstein in July 2019.
